Usage: set_pulse_clock_max_transition [-help] <transition_limit> <object_list>
                                      [-fall] [-rise] [-transitive_fanout]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<transition_limit>     # Transition limit value (float, required)
<object_list>          # List of objects: pulse generator cells, pulse
                       # generator library cells, clocks or current_design
                       # (string, required)
-fall                  # Transition limit value is set for falling transition
                       # (bool, optional)
-rise                  # Transition limit value is set for rising transition
                       # (bool, optional)
-transitive_fanout     # Transition limit value for transitive fanout
                       # (bool, optional)